{"word":"ἐπιγλωσσάομαι","slug":"ἐπιγλωσσάομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐπιγλωσσάομαι</b></el> <el>(attic <el>-ττάομαι</el>) </el><p/><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a>, <i>to throw forth ill language, utter abuse</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>: <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a> <i>to vent reproaches against</i> a person, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:γλῶσσα'><el>γλῶσσα</el></a>\n"}]}